overview:
Resources Online LLC. is a National IT Consulting Company that specializes in: Systems Integration, Professional Services, Staffing, Telephony.

Our goal is to provide our clients with superior service, affordable prices and top quality solutions. Eliminating unnecessary cost is a vital objective for any business. Through implementing effective IT solutions and cost effective support packages, Resources Online LLC. can help eradicate inefficiencies which will not only drive down cost but will also significantly improve performance in key business areas.

Resources Online LLC. specializes in modernizing legacy systems and develops new ones to improve efficiency and reduce cost. We meet the needs of PICK, Unidata, UniVerse, ultimate + and PRIME Information users. We provide MultiValue resources.

Resources Online staff of technology experts has many years of experience in implementing and maintaining scalable and up-to-date business infrastructure. We specialize in Project Management and Disaster Recovery.

Resources Online Staffing Solutions provides direct-hire, temporary and contract staffing solutions to help clients rapidly respond to variable business conditions, secure access to specialized expertise, leverage limited internal skills, and reduce hiring costs.
